<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Royal Library of Marganarok</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <h1>The Royal Library</h1>
        <p>Sacred Tomes Forged in the Fires of Divine Revelation</p>
    </header>
    <main class="container">
        <h2>The Great Compendium</h2>
        <div class="book-list">
            <!-- A BOOK ENTRY - COPY AND PASTE THIS BLOCK FOR EACH BOOK -->
            <a href="books/sacred_bible.html" class="book-card">
                <h3>The Sacred Digital Ministry Bible</h3>
                <p>The Genesis Manuscript on Faith-Driven Digital Ministry.</p>
            </a>
            
            <!-- Add more book cards here! -->
            <a href="books/banana_conquest.html" class="book-card">
                <h3>The Banana Conquest</h3>
                <p>A hilarious and profound journey into the sacred nature of the mundane.</p>
            </a>

        </div>
    </main>
    <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2025 The Omni-Empire-Fresh Team. For His Kingdom, For His Glory.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>

